# Use TypeScript

Write all code in TypeScript. Avoid plain JavaScript (`.js`).

## Guidelines

- Use `.ts` for source files, `.tsx` for React/Svelte components with TypeScript
- Add explicit types for function parameters and return values when inference is unclear
- Prefer `interface` or `type` for object shapes instead of `any`

## Examples

```typescript
// ❌ BAD - untyped
function process(data) {
  return data.items.map(i => i.value);
}

// ✅ GOOD
function process(data: { items: { value: string }[] }): string[] {
  return data.items.map(i => i.value);
}
```
